                                  REQUIREMENTS

You will need the DBus, Glade, GObject, GTK and XDG Python modules.
On Debian-based systems these are available in the following packages:

* python-dbus
* python-glade2
* python-gobject
* python-gtk2
* python-xdg

                               BUILD REQUIREMENTS

You will need the gettext and intltool tools.
On Debian-based systems these are available in the following packages:

* gettext
* intltool

